            "type": "text",
            "text": "Integrating the ACE-Step 1.5 Turbo API requires a solid grasp of its endpoints, authentication mechanisms, and performance characteristics. This guide provides actionable insights for experienced API teams to deploy and manage this model effectively in production environments."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Getting Started with the ACE-Step 1.5 Turbo API"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To begin, obtain your API key from the dashboard. The base URL for all requests is "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "https://api.acestep.com/v1.5/turbo",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Ensure you include the key in the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Authorization",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " header as "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Bearer YOUR_API_KEY",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Here's a basic curl example:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code_block",
        "lang": "bash",
        "value": "curl -X POST https://api.acestep.com/v1.5/turbo/completions \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"prompt\": \"Your input text\", \"max_tokens\": 100}'",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "curl -X POST https://api.acestep.com/v1.5/turbo/completions \\"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "  -H \"Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY\" \\"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "  -d '{\"prompt\": \"Your input text\", \"max_tokens\": 100}'"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
